user.description:
I was attracted towards the software industry after I completed my 12th. After that, I was looking out for opportunities in computer science. I came to know about Masai School and decided to join it as I was interested in full-stack web development.
Masai provides military type coding bootcamp to learn MERN stack. At Masai, I am learning JavaScript, Express.js, Node.js, HTML, MongoDB,React,Redux,CSS. Apart from these technical skills, I am also learning English communication and other soft skills.
If you would like to know more, reach out at chandudeore2016@gmail.com.
